text: Lee Gi-yeol (born 29 February 1940) is a South Korean wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman middleweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of South Korea Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
